trans-unit.source: Represents the length of elements that explicitly support <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Star" /> unit types.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Star" /> 단위 형식을 명시적으로 지원하는 요소의 길이를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Elements such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> use this type to describe width and height in order to support variable distribution of available space.
trans-unit.target: 와 같은 요소 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ColumnDefinition> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.RowDefinition> 이 유형을 사용 하 여 사용 가능한 공간의 변수 배포를 지원 하기 위해 너비와 높이 설명 합니다.

trans-unit.source: XAML Attribute Usage
XAML Values
*doubleLength*

The element’s length, described as either a <xref:System.Double> value that specifies a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_dipixel#plural](~/includes/tlasharptla-dipixelsharpplural-md.md)] measure, or as a *qualifiedDouble* (see below).
trans-unit.target: 로 설명 하는 요소의 길이 <xref:System.Double> 지정 하는 값을 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_dipixel#plural](~/includes/tlasharptla-dipixelsharpplural-md.md)] 측정값을로 *도* (아래 참조).

trans-unit.source: *autoValue*
The element's length, described by either the value Auto or *.
trans-unit.target: 자동 값으로 나타낸 요소의 길이 또는 * 합니다.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Windows.GridUnitType> for more information on the values Auto and *.
trans-unit.target: 참조 <xref:System.Windows.GridUnitType> 자동 값에 대 한 자세한 내용은 및 * 합니다.

trans-unit.source: *qualifiedDouble*
A *double* value as described above for any of the measures, followed by one of the following unit declaration strings: `px`, `in`, `cm`, `pt`.
trans-unit.target: A *double* 단위 선언 문자열 중 하나에 의해 뒤의 측정값에 대해 위에서 설명한 것 처럼 값: `px`, `in`, `cm`, `pt`합니다.

trans-unit.source: `px` (default) is [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_dipixel#plural](~/includes/tlasharptla-dipixelsharpplural-md.md)]
`in` is inches; 1in==96px
`cm` is centimeters; 1cm==(96/2.54) px
`pt` is points; 1pt==(96/72) px
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure.
The number of device-independent pixels (96 pixels-per-inch).
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure using the specified absolute value in pixels.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 픽셀 단위 절대값을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 구조체의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="Pixels" /> is equal to <see cref="F:System.Double.NegativeInfinity" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.PositiveInfinity" />, or <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="Pixels" />가 <see cref="F:System.Double.NegativeInfinity" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.PositiveInfinity" /> 또는 <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />인 경우

trans-unit.source: The initial value of this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" /> held by this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure and specifies what kind of value it holds.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 구조체의 새 인스턴스를 초기화하고 보유할 값의 종류를 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is equal to <see cref="F:System.Double.NegativeInfinity" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.PositiveInfinity" />, or <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" />가 <see cref="F:System.Double.NegativeInfinity" />, <see cref="F:System.Double.PositiveInfinity" /> 또는 <see cref="F:System.Double.NaN" />인 경우

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> that holds a value whose size is determined by the size properties of the content object.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 개체의 크기 속성에 따라 크기가 결정되는 값을 보유하는 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />의 인스턴스를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> whose <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> property is set to <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Auto" />.
Determines whether two <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structures are equal.
The object to compare with the current instance.
Determines whether the specified object is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 개체가 현재 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 인스턴스와 같은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified object has the same value and <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" /> as the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 개체의 값과 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" />이 현재 인스턴스와 같으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure to compare with the current instance.
Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정한 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />가 현재 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />와 같은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> has the same value and <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> as the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />의 값과 <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" />이 현재 인스턴스와 같으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a hash code for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure.
Gets the associated <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
One of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" /> values.
The default is <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Auto" />.
Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> holds a value that is expressed in pixels.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />가 픽셀 단위로 나타낸 값을 보유하는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> property is <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Pixel" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> holds a value whose size is determined by the size properties of the content object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />가 보유하는 값의 크기가 콘텐츠 개체의 크기 속성에 따라 결정되는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> property is <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Auto" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> 속성이 <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Auto" />이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default <xref:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType%2A> value is <xref:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Auto?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
Therefore, this property returns `true` if you do not specify a <xref:System.Windows.GridUnitType> when creating the instance.
trans-unit.target: 따라서이 속성은 반환 `true` 지정 하지 않는 경우는 <xref:System.Windows.GridUnitType> 인스턴스를 만들 때.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> holds a value that is expressed as a weighted proportion of available space.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />가 가중치에 따른 여유 공간에 대한 비율로 나타낸 값을 보유하는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> property is <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Star" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.GridLength.GridUnitType" /> 속성이 <see cref="F:System.Windows.GridUnitType.Star" />이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The first instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> to compare.
The second instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> to compare.
Compares two <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structures for equality.
trans-unit.target: 두 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 구조체가 같은지 여부를 비교합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two instances of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> have the same value and <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 두 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 인스턴스의 값과 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" />이 서로 같으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The first instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> to compare.
The second instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> to compare.
Compares two <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structures to determine if they are not equal.
trans-unit.target: 두 개의 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 구조체를 비교하여 같지 않은지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two instances of <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> do not have the same value and <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 두 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> 인스턴스의 값과 <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridUnitType" />이 서로 다르면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.String" /> representation of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" />.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> representation of the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.GridLength" /> structure.
